rating_comment: It was a fantastic place to stay. Mrs. Nigar is a wonderful host. Her behaviour and attitude was 5 out of 5. The location is ideal for moving both in new and old Dhaka. Considering the price, the home is a great deal. Hopefully a water filter and a washing machine will be established soon. My best wishes!
Good place to stay with family at a reasonable price.
